headline: Snap-on Q1 Earnings on Deck: Will Strong Business Trends Drive a Beat?
summary: SNA's first-quarter results are likely to reflect the benefits of strong business trends, fueled by its value-driven strategy, ongoing innovation and strength in automotive repair.
